## Anti-pattern: Runtime Database Detection

❌ Do NOT do this:

```go
// In handler or middleware:
if adapter.(*timescaledb.Adapter) != nil {
	// timescaledb-specific logic
}
```

✓ Instead, use interface methods that adapters override:

```go
// Handler calls the interface method
result := adapter.TimeBucketClause(r)  // Adapter implementation differs; handler doesn't care
```
